<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; display: inline !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/8420400_1548819297.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">我们为什么关注历史？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">贝奈戴托·克罗齐告诉你：</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">史家对以往史实的兴趣，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">永远与他对当前生活的兴趣连成一体。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">一切历史都是当代史。&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">历史中最值得关注的是什么？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">如果把历史比作一场无止境的戏剧，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">最吸引人的往往是作为主演的英雄豪杰，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">或是组成核心情节的权谋战争。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">然而，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">最不容错过，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">却又最容易错过的是——</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">作为</span>&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">舞台背景</span>&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">的</span>&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">经济</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">有时，主角还未替换，舞台却已悄悄改变，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">直到某一刻，天地焕然一新，人们才惊觉：</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">新的时代已经来临！</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">如何正确观看这一场历史大戏？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▽</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▼</span></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; fo