<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; display: inline !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/8420400_1548819297.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">我们为什么关注历史？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">贝奈戴托·克罗齐告诉你：</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">史家对以往史实的兴趣，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">永远与他对当前生活的兴趣连成一体。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">一切历史都是当代史。&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">历史中最值得关注的是什么？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">如果把历史比作一场无止境的戏剧，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">最吸引人的往往是作为主演的英雄豪杰，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">或是组成核心情节的权谋战争。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">然而，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">最不容错过，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">却又最容易错过的是——</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">作为</span>&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">舞台背景</span>&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">的</span>&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">经济</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">有时，主角还未替换，舞台却已悄悄改变，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">直到某一刻，天地焕然一新，人们才惊觉：</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">新的时代已经来临！</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">如何正确观看这一场历史大戏？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▽</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▼</span></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"></a></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/31362400_1548819297.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="经济-06.jpg" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">带你回顾8个历史朝代&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">畅想10大经济迷思</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;"></span></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;这次“思途”你将听到&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center;"></span><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; display: inline !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/57318400_1548819297.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;你将获得&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700; text-align: center;"></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">中国古代史脉络再梳理</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">重要历史节点经济视角深度剖析</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">先秦 汉 隋 唐 宋 元 明 清</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">土地 盐铁 水利 交通 贸易 都会 农业 殖民&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">扭转固有思维</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">从已知的名词挖掘未知的思考</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">“普天之下莫非王土”，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">中国历代王朝土地究竟国有还是私有？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">两千年前的辩论</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">竟已经暗含了财政学的核心问题？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">工业革命之前人类社会最庞大的水利工程</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">是“大功臣”么？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">言必称汉唐，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">唐朝何以成为最开放的帝国？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">&nbsp;古代中国都市是政治的还是经济的，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">马克斯·韦伯错了么？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">今天中国的经济重心为何在南方，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">宋代竟是转折点？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">郑和的航海成就要从“蒙古时代”说起？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">墨西哥、智利的银矿开采，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;">居然能导致东方的货币革命？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">哥伦布地理大发现之后，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">清成了中国古代唯一人口稳定过亿的王朝</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">鸦片战争的导火索，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">究竟是鸦片还是白银？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">十余本经典研究著作延伸阅读推荐</span>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; color: rgb(165, 165, 165); font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《编户齐民：传统政治社会结构之形成》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《秦制研究》《中国经济思想史（三册）》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;《中国盐业史》《大运河的变迁》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《清代漕运》《丝绸之路新史》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《隋唐两京考》《宋代江南经济史研究》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《中国都市史》</span><span style="text-align: center;">《马可波罗与中外关系》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《郑和下西洋资料汇编》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《银线：19世纪的世界与中国》</span></p><p style="text-align:center;line-height:150%"><br/><span style="line-height: 150%; color: rgb(165, 165, 165); font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"></span></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;你该来听&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">乐于思考的<strong>历史粉</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">经济话题<strong>爱好者</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">需要补充知识、加深理解、拓展思维的<strong>学生党</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">希望培养孩子兴趣与思维能力的<strong>父母</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">以及——</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">渴望从历史思考当下的<strong>所有人</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;来自学界的推荐&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/75768100_1548819297.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">订阅须知：</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;">1. 《帝王与巨商——从十个经济关键词看古代中国》&nbsp;为付费音频专栏，全部11期内容1月30日一次更新完毕；</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><div></div><p class="p1"><span class="s1">2. </span>已购买内容可在本公号均可收听或阅读；</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">3. &nbsp;</span>请理解本专栏作为虚拟服务内容，购买成功后将不接受退款请求；</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">4. &nbsp;</span>严禁任何形式的翻录或转载，严禁在第三方平台传播，违者将追究法律责任；<span class="s1">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">5.&nbsp;</span>订阅或付费过程中有任何问题，请公号后台留言，联系客服。</p><p style="line-height:150%"><br/></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><