(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;来自学界的推荐&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/75768100_1548819297.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">订阅须知：</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;">1. 《帝王与巨商——从十个经济关键词看古代中国》&nbsp;为付费音频专栏，全部11期内容1月30日一次更新完毕；</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><div></div><p class="p1"><span class="s1">2. </span>已购买内容可在本公号均可收听或阅读；</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">3. &nbsp;</span>请理解本专栏作为虚拟服务内容，购买成功后将不接受退款请求；</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">4. &nbsp;</span>严禁任何形式的翻录或转载，严禁在第三方平台传播，违者将追究法律责任；<span class="s1">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">5.&nbsp;</span>订阅或付费过程中有任何问题，请公号后台留言，联系客服。</p><p style="line-height:150%"><br/></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><